title: New Machine Learning Algorithms
sql:
-- Explicit Semantic Analysis (ESA)
insert into esa_settings (setting_name, setting_value)
values ('ESAS_EMBEDDINGS',     'ESAS_EMBEDDINGS_ENABLE'),
       ('ESAS_EMBEDDING_SIZE', 256);

-- XGBoost
insert into xgb_settings (setting_name, setting_value)
values ('monotone_decrease_constraints', 'A1_SEPAL_WIDTH,A3_PETAL_WIDTH'),
       ('interaction_constraints',       '[[A1_SEPAL_WIDTH,A3_PETAL_WIDTH]]'),
       ('eval_metric',                   'aft-nloglik'),
       ('objective',                     'survival:aft'),
       ('aft_loss_distribution',         'normal'),
       ('aft_loss_distribution_scale',   1.20),
       ('aft_right_bound_column_name',   'rbound_col');

-- GLM
insert into glm_settings (setting_name, setting_value)
values ('GLMS_LINK_FUNCTION', 'GLMS_CLOGLOG_LINK');

-- EM
insert into em_settings (setting_name, setting_value)
values ('EMCS_OUTLIER_RATE', 0.05);
